<p><font color="red"><font face="Verdana"><em><em><font color="#007e46" size="2" face="Verdana"><em><font color="#ff0010" face="Verdana"><em><font color="#0000ff"><font face="Verdana"><em><font color="#002cfd" face="Verdana">Aarzel niet mijn boetiek te bezoeken en onder te brengen bij voorkeurverkopers (Le Mystère Enchanté).&nbsp;<a href="http://stores.befr.ebay.be/Le-Mystere-Enchante?_rdc=1" target="_blank"><font size="3" face="Times New Roman">http://stores.befr.ebay.be/Le-Mystere-Enchante?_rdc=1</font></a></font></em><em><font color="#ff0010" face="Verdana"></font></em></font></font></em></font></em></font></em></em></font></font></p>
<p><font color="red"><font face="Verdana"><em><em><font color="#007e46" size="2" face="Verdana"><em><font color="#ff0010" face="Verdana"><em><font color="#0000ff"><font face="Verdana"><em><font color="#ff0010" face="Verdana"></font></em><strong><u>BEOORDELING (FEEDBACK)</u>&nbsp;:</strong></font></font></em></font></em></font></em></em></font></font></p>
